                                        <br />
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p class="pt-000000e4ee7b1c-b356-4ff0-80ed-f0e46b4b0f22" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(α=\sqrt{\frac{{K}_{a}}{C}}\times 100\%=\sqrt{\frac{6.4\times {10}^{-5}}{0.01}}\times 100\%\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-000001e4ee7b1c-b356-4ff0-80ed-f0e46b4b0f22"> </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-000000e4ee7b1c-b356-4ff0-80ed-f0e46b4b0f22 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-000001e4ee7b1c-b356-4ff0-80ed-f0e46b4b0f22 {font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p><p class="pt-0000007ee00bae-7747-4360-b49c-b8eb2a0633f9" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><span class="math-tex" style="font-family: Cambria Math !important;" xmlns="">\(=8\times {10}^{-2}\times 100\%=8\%\) </span><span xml:space="preserve" class="pt-0000017ee00bae-7747-4360-b49c-b8eb2a0633f9">  </span><style>span { white-space: pre-wrap; }p.pt-0000007ee00bae-7747-4360-b49c-b8eb2a0633f9 {line-height: 108%;margin-top: 0;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;}span.pt-0000017ee00bae-7747-4360-b49c-b8eb2a0633f9 {font-family: Times New Roman;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;margin: 0;padding: 0;}</style></p></span>
